Incoming Push Video SDK API 1.3.13

The Push Video SDK Android API provides the ability to configure Push Video notifications, advertising support, and access information managed by the Incoming SDK.

See: Description

Packages 
Package Description
com.incoming.pvnsdk
Implementations of the API interfaces described in com.incoming.pvnsdk.
The Push Video SDK Android API provides the ability to configure Push Video notifications, advertising support, and access information managed by the Incoming SDK. com.incoming.pvnsdk.PusVideo is used to configure and start the Push Video Notification SDK, as described in the integration instructions.
